isLocaleSupportedByDevice.!doc:
This API enables you to verify whether a locale is supported by a device.
        @param {String} locale  Specifies the locale that must be verified if it is supported by the device.Locale must be in one of the following formats:language_countryCode, language. <b>Mandatory</b>
