     @param {Boolean} positionoptions.requestModifyLocationSettings When you set this parameter to true, if the app cannot fetch location updates due to inadequate location settings on the device, the system automatically invokes a dialog box that helps the user enable the necessary location settings with a single tap.
     @param {Boolean} positionoptions.requireBackgroundAccess Set to true to fetch the device location updates even when the app is running in the background.
     @param {Number} positionoptions.timeout Denotes the maximum length of time in milliseconds that is allowed to pass from the call.


@Available All platforms.
