	@param {Number} radius  Specifies the radius of the clipping shape. Represents the corner radius of the rounded rectangular shape when clipping shape is VIEW_CLIP_SHAPE_ROUNDED_RECTANGLE or represents the radius of circle when clipping shape is VIEW_CLIP_SHAPE_CIRCLE.
