onTouchEnd.!doc:
An event callback is invoked by the platform when the user touch is released from the touch surface. This event is invoked asynchronously.
@param {widgetref} source  Handle to the widget reference on which the scrolling is in progress.<b>Optional</b>
@param {Number} x Specifies the X co-ordinate with in the widget with respect to widget's co-ordinate system. It is a number indicating device independent pixel.<b>Optional</b>
