	 @param {Array.<objects>} contenLayers  Array of two JS Objects. Each JS Object contains following key-value pairs to define a layer for ripple background. You can define background for the ripple as a skin or as a background color.
	 @param {Constant} paddingMode Defines how layer padding should affect the bounds of subsequent layers. You can define: RIPPLE_PADDING_MODE_NEST: Nests each layer inside padding of the previous layer, RIPPLE_PADDING_MODE_STACK: Stacks each layer top of the previous layer. This is the default value.
